data.description: Welcome to desirable McAllister Meadows! This spacious 3bd, 2.5bath home offers open-concept living w/ gourmet kitchen, granite countertops, large island, and a gas range! French doors leading into the bonus office/den, loads of storage and natural light. Enjoy entertaining in the formal dining room or get cozy by the fireplace in the living room. A large covered patio, garden beds, and fenced side yard are perfect for those who enjoy the outdoors. Roomy primary bedroom with an oversized walk-in closet and dreamy well-appointed ensuite. This absolutely immaculate home boasts easy access to I-5, JBLM, great schools as well as neighborhood disc golf, paved trails & wetland wildlife!
